{"serial": "31002", "department_serial": 33, "code": "EI1102", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Introduction to Energy and Materials Science", "ch": "能源與材料科學導論"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Lee, Sheng-Wei"], "ch": ["李勝偉"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 5, "session": ["5", "6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "E6", "room": "A127"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "工學院學士班", "en": "Interdisciplinary Program of Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 2, "selected": 20, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "1. 理解材料科學與能量技術的基本概念。\n2. 掌握原子鍵結、晶體結構和晶體缺陷的基本知識。\n3. 了解相圖及其在微觀結構發展中的應用。\n4. 認識太陽能轉換技術及能量儲存技術的基本原理及應用。", "en": "1. Understand the fundamental concepts of materials science and energy technology.\n2. Acquire basic knowledge of atomic bonding, crystal structures, and crystal defects.\n3. Comprehend phase diagrams and their applications in microstructural development.\n4. Recognize the basic principles and applications of solar energy conversion and energy storage technologies."}, "outline": {"ch": "1. 能量技術與材料科學導論\n能源技術在現代社會中的重要性。\n材料科學在能源技術中的應用。\n2. 原子鍵合與晶體結構\n從原子到固體的轉變。\n價電子與內核電子，鍵合力的類型。\n空間晶格與單位晶胞。\n原胞與原始晶胞，七大晶系，14種布拉維晶格與點群。\nWigner Seitz晶胞、配位數。\n晶體中的平面與方向，密勒指數，術語，晶面間距，晶體方向。\nX射線衍射及其應用。\n3. 晶體缺陷與擴散\n固溶體、點缺陷、線缺陷與面缺陷。\n非晶固體與擴散概念的探討。\n4. 相圖與平衡微觀結構發展\n相律及相圖的基本原理。\n槓桿法則與緩慢冷卻過程中的微觀結構發展。\n5. 太陽能轉換技術\n太陽能轉換為電能的原理。\n太陽能電池的製備工藝與應用。\n6. 能量儲存技術\n鋰離子電池、燃料電池及其他儲能設備的工作原理。\n能量儲存設備的製備工藝與應用。", "en": ". Introduction of Energy Technology and Material Science\n2. Atomic Bonding and Crystal Structure\nFrom atoms to solids, Valence and Core Electron, Types of Binding Forces Space Lattices Unit Cell, Primitive Cell, The Seven Systems, 14 Bravais (space) Lattices, and Point Groups Wigner Seitz Cell, Coordination Number, Planes and Directions in Crystals, Miller Indices, Terminology, Spacing Between Planes, Directions in Crystals, X-Ray Diffraction.\n3. Crystal Defects and Diffusion\nSolid Solution, Point Defects, Linear Defects, Planar Defects,  Noncrystalline Solids and concept of diffusion.\n4. Phase Diagrams - Equilibrium Microstructural Development\nThe Phase Rule, The Phase Diagram, The Lever Rule, Microstructural Development During Slow Cooling.\n5. Solar Energy Conversion Technology\nSolar to electricity; Working principle, Fabrication process, Applications.\n6. Energy Storage Technology Lithium ion Battery, fuel cell and other storage devices; Working principle; Fabrication process; Applications."}, "textbook": {"ch": "Callister, W.D., ＆ Rethwisch, D.G. (2018). Materials Science and Engineering: An Introduction (10th ed.). Wiley.", "en": "Callister, W.D., ＆ Rethwisch, D.G. (2018). Materials Science and Engineering: An Introduction (10th ed.). Wiley."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "50", "en": "50"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "作業與課堂參與：30％\n期中考試：40％\n期末考試：30％", "en": "Homeworks and Class Participation: 30％\nMidterm Exam: 40％\nntsFinal Exam: 30％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "學習能力－獨立自主地獲取知識、不斷更新知識的能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}, {"competencies": "運用方法能力－能夠運用方法學的思維解決不同情境下的問題", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}, {"competencies": "創新能力－運用創造性思維發現和解決問題的能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}, {"competencies": "活用工具之能力－熟練運用外語、程式語言、軟體等現代工具的能力", "rating": "(2)低", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}, {"competencies": "實踐能力－將知識運用於具體生活實際的能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}, {"competencies": "表達能力－能夠運用各種工具，並以口語、影音、書面等不同型式表達概念或結果", "rating": "(1)非常低", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "團隊合作能力－能夠在團隊中與不同領域同伴溝通、表達、協調、共同合作與計畫管理的能力", "rating": "(1)非常低", "assesments": ["作業練習", 